                            <comment id="12595026" author="jimk" created="Wed, 7 May 2008 20:23:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;HbaseRPC$Invoker.invoke was declared as throws Throwable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Modified to add try / catch block around client.call to catch Throwable If what is caught is an instanceof IOException, it is simply rethrown. Otherwise a new IOException is created and the Throwable is set as the cause.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
